code: @Override protected SlackAccount createAccount(String name, Settings accountSettings) {     return new SlackAccount(name, accountSettings, httpClient, logger). }
private static List<Setting<?>> getDynamicSettings() {     return Arrays.asList(SETTING_DEFAULT_ACCOUNT, SETTING_DEFAULTS). }
private static List<Setting<?>> getSecureSettings() {     return Arrays.asList(SETTING_URL_SECURE). }

public static List<Setting<?>> getSettings() {     List<Setting<?>> allSettings = new ArrayList<Setting<?>>(getDynamicSettings()).     allSettings.addAll(getSecureSettings()).     return allSettings. }
